Yara on windows:
find all mal lnk files in malware-samples folders and its subfolders
  >yara64.exe LNK_Ruleset.yar -r c:\malware-samples\
  >yara64.exe rules\RTF-rules\apt_royalroad.yar -r c:\malware-samples
  
